# Format: <type>(<scope>): <subject>
#
# type  : feat | fix | docs | style | refactor | perf | test | chore | release
# scope : optional, e.g. auth | api | cli | agent | gateway | mesh | storage
# subject: imperative, lowercase, no period at end
#
# Examples:
#   feat(cli): add OAuth2 token refresh command
#   fix(agent): handle empty vault response gracefully
#   chore: bump version to 2.5.0
#   release: v2.5.0
#
# Body (optional — blank line after subject):
#   Explain *what* and *why*, not *how*. Wrap at 72 chars.
#
# Footer (optional):
#   Breaking change: BREAKING CHANGE: <description>
#   Closes issue:    Closes #123
#
# Branch-to-merge target reminder:
#   feature/*  →  develop   (PR + squash merge)
#   hotfix/*   →  main + develop (PR + merge commit)
#   release/*  →  main + develop (PR + merge commit, then tag)
#
